onionbalance (0.2.4) unstable; urgency=medium

  * New upstream release
  * Updated Debian packaging, by importing the debian/ folder upstream,
    cleaning and improving it to be in sync with the current codebase.
    Details at https://gitlab.torproject.org/tpo/onion-services/onionbalance/-/issues/46
